ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of DAWN S. DALLEY of Conception Bay South, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Richard J. Daw, whose term has expired.
